{"tid":1721993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭數月 勿忘初心 - 民間記者會聲明","createTime":"2019-11-14T20:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:42:02.000Z","uid":325953,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"39fcdbfd4d21f6b6e508dddd559dbea0c55f460e","tid":1721993,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:36:38.000Z","msg":"過去數天，守護中大的手足以「不自由、毋寧死」的風骨，奮力抵抗魔警攻城，決心對抗暴政。二橋守衛戰之勝利，振奮士氣，令抗爭望見曙光。<br />\n<br />\n全港抗爭必須乘勝追擊，旭日行動如箭在弦，大三罷行動絕不止息。不論區選舉辦與否，香港人仍決心抗爭，毋懼政權以此作脅，直到五大訴求全部落實。<br />\n<br />\n「不分化、不割蓆」是抗爭賴以持續的基石。只要抗爭者團結一致，開路之主導權始終在人民手上。三罷抗爭，全民皆兵，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會<br />\n2019年11月15日旭日初升前"},{"pid":"ac02fa9e2dc937cd7866fad2ce3e1290bc18c391","tid":1721993,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e003ddd6ce0f0d3b135a3ed964b14d0739f016ae","tid":1721993,"uid":256019,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:38:17.000Z","msg":"支持！到我死一刻都絕不分化、絕不割蓆！"},{"pid":"6e5d2038c6b28979cf97cc417a227425fcbf946b","tid":1721993,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:38:33.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b0a1b1304a8743044b0e6982d5cdb2cbf8cd434f","tid":1721993,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T20:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e8291e6e12082c5804db0d3e80c0694c85a72d","tid":1721993,"uid":47091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"